<div class="hero-unit">
  <h1>Bloccit</h1>
  <p>Bloccit is a resource for sharing links with your friends!</p>
  <p>
      <%= link_to "Sign In", new_user_session_path, class: 'btn btn-primary btn-large' %> or 
      <%= link_to "Sign Up", new_user_registration_path, class: 'btn btn-primary btn-large' %> today!
  </p>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="span4">
    <h2>Join Bloccit</h2>
    <p>Bloccit by BJ is really good fun! Make blog posts, have friends comment and share your vision of how society should be with the entire world!</p>
  </div>
  <div class="span4">
    <h2>Tell Your Friends</h2>
    <p>Why talk directly to your friends when you can Bloccit with them! Bloccit renders one-to-one communication redundant with its efficient way of letting you dump your thoughts on all your friends in one post!</p>
  </div>
  <div class="span4">
    <h2>Write about stuff!</h2>
    <p>Live your life through Bloccit! Say you've done this, say you've done that - you're real friends will know it a load of rubbish, but in the internet age you don't need real friends</p>
  </div>
</div>